Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_28_1,I didn't expect there to be a place like this beneath Rabelle College.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_28_2,"Before Sundermere base was built, this was a research facility for Augmented Resonance Effects and Void Storm countermeasures. It's been decommissioned for years."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_28_3,The Executive Committee told me I could do whatever I wanted with the space. So I used my Forte to do some light remodeling.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_28_4,"Memories of my students that should exist only in my mind, here... they become real. A tangible piece to display."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_28_5,You're using your Forte to do all this? How long did it take you to create this?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_28_6,"However long it took, it was worth it... So the ones who ""stay"" don't just stay, and the ones who ""leave"" don't just leave."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_28_7,"We still have some time. If you're interested, feel free to look around."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_29_1,The exhibits we're looking for are here.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_29_2,Hmm? Behind the wall?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_29_3,"Don't forget, this is my Memory Palace. Naturally, memory locks require memory keys to unlock."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_29_4,Allow me to demonstrate—This fancy trick only works in this little domain of mine.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_31_1,This is the very reason I built this exhibition hall in the first place.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_31_2,What is it?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_31_3,"Professor, do you trust me?"
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_31_4,I...
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_31_5,Lucilla?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_31_6,You spaced out there. Are you alright?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_31_7,I'm fine. Just had a dream that only lasted a few seconds. Rather fascinating.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_31_8,Maybe it's a good idea to rest before the review starts?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_31_9,"Don't worry. I promise you I'll crash the second this is over. But right now, we must bring these exhibits with us."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_31_10,Will a few exhibits be enough to sway them?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_31_11,...
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_31_12,"(She usually knows exactly how to sell anything, so why does she look so hesitant now?)"
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_31_17,Thank you for your trust. I know you have a thousand questions burning in your mind.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_31_18,"""How will she handle the New Fed?"" ""What's her plan for the Synchronists with the Exostrider gone?"" Forgive me for not having the answers just yet."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_31_19,I know you'd never harm the students. That's the only answer I need.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_31_20,"I... Terrible timing for a compliment, {PlayerName}."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_31_21,Anyway. Let's take these two exhibits and—
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_31_22,"See you soon, Professor."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_31_23,Some kind of force pulled us down here. Do you know where we are?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_31_24,"If my memory serves, we're directly beneath the exhibition hall."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_31_25,This way.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_33_1,A Synchronist's cockpit? Was this the prototype?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_33_2,"It looks the part, but this was actually our ""Plan B."" Designed without safety limiters to get sync rates up quick. Lets a Synchronist pilot the Exostrider by force."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_33_3,...
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_33_4,"I know, I know. It was meant as a last resort if civilization was staring down extinction. The project was terminated after the initial trials."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_33_5,"The Synchronists who volunteered... In the end, they lost their ability to resonate with the Exostrider ever again."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_33_6,What our students are facing now isn't new.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_33_7,I just hope I can do better by them this time.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_34_1,What's happening?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_34_2,"Something rather unpleasant, I imagine."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_34_3,Lucilla...
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_34_4,"Fine, no more jokes. Honestly, anyone watching would think you're the one facing the board. There, there, I know the way out."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_34_5,Remember what I told you before entering the Dark Side? About the memories I erase periodically that can never be recovered?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_34_6,"Some things... I can't bear to remember, but I also can't bear to forget, so I store them here. Looks like some of them are tired of being locked up..."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_34_7,"{PlayerName}, look up. The exit is right above. We can use this <ano=Photo>key</ano> to leave. But I need your help to get there."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_34_8,"Everything here is from my memory, but I know <i>you</i> are real. And wherever you are, that must be reality."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_34_9,I understand. I'll be your reference point. But what about that girl? Are we just leaving her?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_34_10,"{PlayerName}, do you have any experience dealing with children? Tell me, what makes a child the most flustered when they're playing hide-and-seek?"
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_34_11,...Ah. I see.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_34_12,"Now, come along. Let's treat this little escape as a warm-up for the review."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_35_1,Welcome to the Anti-Voidmatter Materials Lab. It's where they first developed the materials for the Academy's Antivoid Canopy.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_35_2,What's all of that in the center of the room?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_35_3,The scrap of the day. Even the best recycling can only keep up with so much.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_35_4,Let's look around to see if there are any leads.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_36_1,Only one in a thousand makes the cut. Which means nine hundred ninety-nine don't.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_36_2,People see the Antivoid Canopy and praise its ingenuity. They'll never get to see the blueprints of the ones who were rejected.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_37_1,Is this artificial Retroact Rain?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_37_2,"Oh, dear me. This is but a pale imitation."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_37_3,"Among the Synchronists who survived the experiments, there was one from Jinzhou. Once he realized he'd never resonate with the Exostrider, he returned home and joined the Ministry of Development's Defense Division."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_37_4,"There, he and his colleagues worked together to develop Jinzhou's Retroact Rain defenses."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_37_5,You're saying the shields against Retroact Rain and Void Storms share the same origin?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_37_6,Not exactly. His approach didn't work on Void Storms at all... and it was discarded. Long ago.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_37_7,"Before he left the Academy, the only things he asked to take with him were a few sheets of material buried under that pile of junk."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_37_8,I often wonder... was he just reluctant to let go of his design? Or had he already mapped out how to protect his hometown?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_37_9,The girl who trapped us here... She must be trying to show us something through this memory.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_37_10,Hmm. Seems I've been getting schooled by my own students a lot lately...
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_37_11,"Let's go. It's time to move on to the next ""classroom."""
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_38_1,"Well... we made quite the headway there, didn't we?"
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_38_2,"That said, I'm glad to see we're at least moving."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_38_3,Let's keep heading upwards. We'll find our way out soon enough.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_39_2,...
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_39_3,What's wrong?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_39_4,"Stay where I can see you, {PlayerName}. We've wandered into an unpleasant memory."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_39_5,It's far too easy to get lost in here...
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_39_6,It doesn't look like there's a way to cross the barrier ahead.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_39_7,Hmm... I have an idea.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_39_8,"{PlayerName}, just go with me on this, alright?"
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_40_1,"Clear as day, Madam. Your daughter isn't sick. She has awakened her Forte, and it's a remarkably rare memory-type."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_40_2,Congratulations! I'm certain she'll make an immense contribution to the New Federation one day.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_40_3,Nonsense! My Luci will never become a Resonator!
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_40_4,Mom...
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_40_5,I don't want to be a Resonator. Please... no!
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_40_6,Luci!
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_41_1,Lucilla?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_41_2,"(Without a ""reference point"", she's getting pulled into the deep end of her memories. I need to find her before too much time passes.)"
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_41_3,Not good.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_1,"Are you still there, Lucilla?"
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_2,Yes.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_3,Then why aren't you answering?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_4,What do you want me to say?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_5,"You can say ""Okay,"" or ""I understand."""
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_6,"This is the perfect moment—while our opponents are spread too thin, we take the reins. Just like the time you became President..."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_7,"Don't worry about the narrative. We'll play the villain. You just act tough, rope the independent auditor in, and we'll force another round of review."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_8,"You fight hard. We express our ""concerns."" And then... we both take a step back. As long as we ensure our control over the future of the Synchronist Program, nothing else matters."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_9,And what do you want from my students?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_10,"Simple. We both get what we want. They have talent, and we help them achieve their dreams. And it'll be their choice."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_11,Their choice? Whose dreams are we really achieving?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_12,"It will be their choice, Lucilla. My Luci. I won't speak of your past choices, but tell me, has there been a single choice that wasn't your own?"
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_13,I still refuse.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_14,"There. Just like that. ""Act tough,"" ""fight hard,"" and then we both ""take a step back"" at the review..."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_15,"From the Academy to the Pioneer Association, then to the Spacetrek Collective, and now here… No wonder I was never cut out to be President."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_16,"Watch out! That's ""me"" from the Dark Side. I used this memory to trap her."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_17,"When are you going to tell {Male=him;Female=her}, Professor Lucilla? President Lucilla? That you've already made a deal with the New Federation?"
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_18,Let's go.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_19,"You think you can outrun yourself, Lucilla?"
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_20,(I need to know the truth.)
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_21,(I trust Lucilla. That's enough.)
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_22,Your plan... Are you just following the New Federation's playbook?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_23,"Don't let her get to you. How could I ever sell out my students? I have a plan, it's just..."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_24,"Before the meeting starts, I need you to take the time to fill me in on what's really happening."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_25,"Thank you. I promise, I'd never let the New Federation lay a single finger on my students. But..."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_26,"That's just her wishful thinking. A moth to the flame, daring the sky with wings of wax."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_27,Your students will die because of you!
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_42_28,"...Let's leave this place, {PlayerName}."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_43_1,Is this it? This is as far as we've got?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_43_2,That just means we'd better pick up the pace.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_44_1,"Once again, I found the courage to step into this room. Time flows here, silent and peaceful, and the Academy is alive and thriving. We've come so much further than I ever dreamed. I wish you were here to see it."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_45_1,Is that Sundermere? Are we back before the Starward Riseway was even built?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_45_2,Most of the students who lost their Synchronist status in those forced sync trials decided to return home. All but one.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_45_3,She told me it wasn't that she'd lost the Exostrider. The Exostrider had lost her.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_45_4,"She said she'd designed a revolutionary transport method.  A ""rocket piercing the sky."" A way to bridge that ""sky"" and the ""earth."""
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_45_5,This was the day she tested it. Her first crewed flight.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_45_6,Then that wasn't a falling star. It was—
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_45_7,A spacecraft. Carrying the most brilliant student I've ever known.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_45_8,"Amiya to Sundermere Lookout. Professor, can you hear me?!"
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_45_9,Yes.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_45_10,"The weather couldn't be more perfect today! Oh, and I just saw a super huge Soliskin! I'll snap a picture for you as soon as I can!"
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_45_11,Okay.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_45_12,Professor? You don't sound like your usual self. Are those investors giving you a hard time again?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_45_13,"No, it's not that. I just... I haven't slept much lately. I'm a little tired. That's all."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_45_14,"...Professor, do you trust us?"
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_45_15,I...
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_45_16,"Hey, remember that old Huanglong saying? ""Know the way at dawn, and... and something-something at dusk?"" Ugh, it went right out of my head!"
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_45_17,I can't remember it either...
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_45_18,That's okay! I'll look it up and tell you the second the experiment is over!
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_45_19,Talk to you soon!
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_45_20,"Please, {PlayerName}..."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_45_21,"From the way it fell, Voidmatter must've pierced the shielding mid-flight. But if we'd reinforced the coating... Hmm..."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_45_22,What kind of civilization do you think built the Exostrider? If they were that advanced... do you think they'd already defeated the Threnodians? Overcome the Lament?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_45_23,"But before they reached the stars, they must have fallen too. Again and again."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_45_24,Go. Be our eyes. Walk with humanity.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_45_25,Please give this to our teacher. Humanity's smallest step... and everything we had to give.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_45_26,This isn't good.
