Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_49_1,"Lucilla, your emotions are affecting this domain! It's dangerous!"
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_49_2,Staying here is the real danger. We have to leave.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_50_1,Almost there.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_50_2,"As long as we keep moving upward, we'll find the way out."
