Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_51_6,What?
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_51_7,You're terrified that your proposal will be their end.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_51_8,You're afraid because you know they'll support any plan you bring to the table.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_51_9,Because you're their teacher.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_51_10,Because no one in this world understands them the way you do.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_51_11,"Another lesson from my own student, huh..."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_51_12,"See you later, {PlayerName}."
