Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_62_1,"The illustrious {PlayerName}. Jinzhou, Ragunna, Septimont... and now Lahai-Roi. Why, of all times, do you choose to remain behind the curtain?"
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_62_2,I don't owe you an explanation.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_62_3,I trust Lucilla.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_62_4,"Hmph. They said you were ""formidable but easily swayed by emotion."" Looks like our intelligence division is full of overpaid deadweight after all."
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_62_5,She understands what her students need better than I ever could.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_62_6,She understands what her students need better than I ever could.
Main_LahaiRoi_WMXZTK_62_7,She's let their childish idealism cloud her judgment.
